feat(games): Add gold-standard games platform with 5 anchor games

- Implement unified games framework with GameShell, StateManager, DifficultyEngine, ExplainabilityEngine
- Add 5 anchor games: Daily Logic Gauntlet, Grid Racer, Draft Duel, Hex, Systems Mastery
- Add comprehensive error boundaries and accessibility (WCAG 2.2 AA)
- Add analytics hooks (dev-only logging, no external services)
- Add reduced motion support and performance monitoring
- All games are 100% client-side, browser-only, no paid APIs
- Add Games Hub with filtering and search
- Add SEO metadata and Open Graph tags
- Add comprehensive documentation

Security: No secrets, no paid APIs, all client-side
Cost: Zero - all games run in browser, no external service calls
